# ▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬
# 💎 NEXUS-1MD MASTER CONFIGURATION
# ▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬

# 👤 1. IDENTITY & SECURITY (MANDATORY)
# --------------------------------------
# SUDO: The Super-Admin number (YOUR number with country code).
# Only this number can use system commands like .update and see credentials.
SUDO=254101010101

# OWNERS: Additional admins separated by commas.
OWNERS=254101010101

# 🔑 2. SESSION & CONNECTION
# --------------------------------------
# SESSION_ID: Your unique bot session (starts with BWM~).
# Get this by scanning the QR code once or from your console.
SESSION_ID=

# PAIRING_NUMBER: (Optional) For connecting without QR code.
PAIRING_NUMBER=

# 🛠️ 3. SYSTEM PREFERENCES
# --------------------------------------
# PREFIX: Command prefix (default is .)
PREFIX=.

# MODE: 'public' or 'private' (default is public)
MODE=public

# 🌐 4. DATABASE & STORAGE (OPTIONAL)
# --------------------------------------
# DATABASE_URL: Your PostgreSQL/MySQL URL (Bot falls back to JSON if empty).
DATABASE_URL=

# 🤖 5. AI & API KEYS
# --------------------------------------
GROQ_API_KEY=
OPENAI_API_KEY=

# ▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬
# ℹ️ IMPORTANT: After filling this, save it as ".env"
# ▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬
